        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued May 2 at 5:03PM EDT until May 2 at 5:15PM EDT by NWS Pittsburgh PA</headline>
        <description>At 503 PM EDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 6 miles northeast
of Weirton, moving east at 35 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and small hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Weirton.
</description>
        <instruction>Seek shelter inside a well-built structure and stay away from
windows. This storm is capable of producing damaging winds.</instruction>
